Do not call this.  See: \*(L"shutdown\*(R" instead.
.PP
\&\fIThis function is deprecated.\fR In new code, use the \*(L"shutdown\*(R" call
instead.
.PP
Deprecated functions will not be removed from the \s-1API\s0, but the fact that
